  "text": "Here we want to study the effects of weak dissipative mechanisms on the slow dynamics across the quantum transition. Therefore, beside the changes of the Hamiltonian parameters, we suppose that the many-body system is also subject to some interaction with the environment. The time dependence of its density matrix ρ can be reasonably described by the Lindblad master equation [CITATION_1] ∂ρ ∂t",
